{"tid":901803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新北祭「美女牌」　長腿政風公僕打頭陣 她們的父親....","createTime":"2018-11-14T09:44:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-14T10:11:03.000Z","uid":72009,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4246f858f3b4cc1626b97b0ef7f035e0ede3f615","tid":901803,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:44:26.000Z","msg":"今天是選舉投票前最後倒數10天，候選人文宣盡出吸引選民注意，新北民政局也特別製作「選舉倒數，出來投票」系列貼圖，由民政美女以甜美笑容及可愛的數字手勢，鼓勵大家11月24日出來投票，即日起一連10天刊出，首張貼圖由政風女公僕秀長腿打頭陣，才一公開，立刻引發網友熱烈迴響討論，貼圖上的倒數10天，大大的阿拉伯「10」還讓人誤以為是10號美女刺客出來參選拉票。<br />\n民政局長江俊霆表示，常收到長輩們在LINE互傳道早安的「問候圖」，民政局也從3年前開始仿效，製作活動、政策、節氣、神明聖誕等業務相關的貼圖，每天早上發送群組，累計已發送近1000張貼圖，不但成為最好的茶餘飯後話題，也因免費又即時，達到很好的宣傳效果。<br />\n江俊霆說，再過10天就是九合一選舉投票日，為鼓勵大家不放棄手中神聖的一票，特別精心製作宣傳「出來投票」貼圖，由同仁化身宣傳大使，以甜美、可愛笑容及選舉倒數天數的手勢，邀請大家一同去投票、投好票，透過選票表達自己的意見，歡迎大家多多轉發。<br />\n擔任首發的政風科員賴家儀說，很開心能擔任宣傳大使，這是她第1次參加公投及縣市長的投票，由於參與地方公職人員的候選人眾多，還有10個公投案，讓人眼花撩亂，她特別仔細閱讀選舉公報，瞭解各候選人的政見，一定要在選舉當天投下自己關鍵的一票。<br />\n江俊霆提醒，11月24日上午8時至下午4時，記得攜帶個人國民身分證、印章及投票通知單，至戶籍地之投開票所投票；每一票都很重要，請大家好好把握手中神聖的一票，踴躍行使公民權利。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/politics/realtime/20181114/1466446\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2Frealtime%2F20181114%2F1466446&d=qu9KdP7lo%2BbjoGHSeUCOTDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=70b35954\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Fpolitics%2Frealtime%2F20181114%2F1466446&h=c19e8115\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/politics/realtime/20181114/1466446</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181114/640_a01ac08f56294fec558d78e07eb9cb95.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181114%2F640_a01ac08f56294fec558d78e07eb9cb95.jpg&h=93ad64ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181114/640_047d0042c0bd36918aa460c70d0ae119.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181114%2F640_047d0042c0bd36918aa460c70d0ae119.jpg&h=cb22413d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n自少由前世情人開發"},{"pid":"bbba6e7ad155ca073f862b283de5e9a59a2db9f4","tid":901803,"uid":28181,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:46:58.000Z","msg":"新北又加一分"},{"pid":"0ad0a474418c4421c13aadc7268b3e51ec1c7c65","tid":901803,"uid":133529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:57:12.000Z","msg":"佢係咪暗示想我捐山窿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce8db07bc7daeaf6eb6df7fcdfc4c9c754fe4eae","tid":901803,"uid":155818,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:57:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"070e7f309d45d3c15d5efda556824830a6b159f2","tid":901803,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:58:58.000Z","msg":"新北美眉: 爸爸，大力Ｄ...全部給我"},{"pid":"28b8e5664713f4f94c87d3a4966f4715d2ce9853","tid":901803,"uid":10382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T10:06:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf9bbedb4f42907d3d73bfc76f49ad1ee64bbe61","tid":901803,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0ad0a474418c4421c13aadc7268b3e51ec1c7c65","tid":901803,"uid":133529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T09:57:12.000Z","msg":"佢係咪暗示想我捐山窿<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-14T10:10:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid